(174, 1, '2018-08-15 15:21:58', '2018-08-15 14:21:58', '<p class=\"p1 copy-l\"><span style=\"color: #00a5db;\">The team at Perrigo has a wealth of experience in quoting for, winning and implementing significant Contract Manufacturing opportunities.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">Having collaborated with major blue chip brands for over 4 decades, in traditional toll manufacturing, contract new product development and supply from in-house Intellectual Property, Perrigos support structure is geared to delivering projects on time and in full. Brands can be assured of a confidential and professional service, with an experienced team and a facility focused on delivering quality affordable healthcare products.</p>', 'Our Story', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '10-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-08-15 15:21:58', '2018-08-15 14:21:58', '', 10, 'http://rarecontent.co.uk/perrigo/10-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
