ion of individuals and families in communities that Perrigo serves.\r\n\r\nIn the UK, we have recently supported the following:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Alcohol Education Trust</li>\r\n 	<li>Barnsley Hospice</li>\r\n 	<li>Barnsley Hospital Charity</li>\r\n 	<li>Barnsley Independent Alzheimers and Dementia Support</li>\r\n 	<li>Barnsley Special Baby Care Unit</li>\r\n 	<li>Bluebell Wood Children\'s Hospice</li>\r\n 	<li>Braunton Academy</li>\r\n 	<li>Braunton Volunteers</li>\r\n 	<li>Braunton</li>\r\n 	<li>British Heart Foundation</li>\r\n 	<li>Calvert Trust Exmoor</li>\r\n 	<li>Cancer Research UK</li>\r\n 	<li>Candlelighters</li>\r\n 	<li>Children\'s Hospital</li>\r\n 	<li>Darton Community College</li>\r\n 	<li>Devon Air Ambulance</li>\r\n 	<li>Devon Diving Research Centre</li>\r\n 	<li>Devon Freewheelers</li>\r\n 	<li>Early Bird Autism</li>\r\n 	<li>Exeter Community Initiative (Ripple Effect Braunton)</li>\r\n 	<li>Macmillan</li>\r\n 	<li>Meanwood Valley Urban Farm</li>\r\n 	<li>NDADA</li>\r\n 	<li>North Devon Hospice</li>\r\n 	<li>Pathfields Activity Centre</li>\r\n 	<li>Pippa Jones Little Treasure Trust</li>\r\n 	<li>RNLI</li>\r\n 	<li>Station House (SHCA)</li>\r\n 	<li>Yorkshire Air Ambulance</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Corporate Social Responsibility', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '18-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-08-15 16:31:45', '2018-08-15 15:31:45', '', 18, 'http://rarecontent.co.uk/perrigo/18-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
