ching charity activities</strong>\r\n\r\nWe know that we have a lot of employees who are very passionate about a charity close to their hearts and want to help support this, which is why we offer a charity matching scheme.\r\n\r\n<strong>4. Volunteer Programme</strong>\r\n\r\nIf our people volunteer their time outside of work to a charitable organisation, we donate money towards that charity.', 'Corporate Social Responsibility', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '18-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-08-20 13:04:55', '2018-08-20 12:04:55', '', 18, 'http://rarecontent.co.uk/perrigo/18-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
